//all n-1 days -> nth day

import util.control.Breaks._

val dataTempTemp = sqlContext.read
    .format("com.databricks.spark.csv")
    .option("header", "true") // Use first line of all files as header
    .option("inferSchema", "true") // Automatically infer data types
    .option("delimiter", ",")
    .load("/data/sidana/purch/experiments/atleast_one/inputData").withColumn("utcdate",unix_timestamp($"utcdate","yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss").cast("timestamp"))
    
val dataTemp = dataTempTemp.select($"userId",$"offerId",dayofyear(dataTempTemp("utcDate")),$"wasClicked").withColumnRenamed("dayofyear(utcDate)","day")
val data = dataTemp.select("day").distinct
val rows = data.collect()
for(row<-rows){
    breakable{
    if(row(0)==35){
        break
    }
    else{
        val today = row(0)
        val yesterday = today.asInstanceOf[Int] - 1
        
        val trainDataTemp = dataTempTemp.filter(dayofyear($"utcDate")<=yesterday)
        
        val goodDataTrain = trainDataTemp.filter(trainDataTemp("wasClicked")===1)
        val groupByUsersOffersTrain = goodDataTrain.select("userId","offerId").distinct
        val groupByUsersTrain = groupByUsersOffersTrain.groupBy("userId").count.withColumnRenamed("userId","userId_e")
        val goodUsersTrain = groupByUsersTrain.filter($"count">=1)
        val trainData = trainDataTemp.join(goodUsersTrain, trainDataTemp("userId")===goodUsersTrain("userId_e")).drop(goodUsersTrain("userId_e")).drop(goodUsersTrain("count")).select("userId","offerId","utcDate","wasClicked").orderBy("utcDate")
        
        
        
        val testDataTemp = dataTempTemp.filter(dayofyear($"utcDate")===today)
        val goodDataTest = testDataTemp.filter(testDataTemp("wasClicked")===1)
        val groupByUsersOffersTest = goodDataTest.select("userId","offerId").distinct
        val groupByUsersTest = groupByUsersOffersTest.groupBy("userId").count.withColumnRenamed("userId","userId_e")
        val goodUsersTest = groupByUsersTest.filter($"count">=1)
        val testData = testDataTemp.join(goodUsersTest, testDataTemp("userId")===goodUsersTest("userId_e")).drop(goodUsersTest("userId_e")).drop(goodUsersTest("count")).select("userId","offerId","utcDate","wasClicked").orderBy("utcDate")
        
        trainData.rdd.coalesce(1,false).saveAsTextFile("/data/sidana/purch/experiments/atleast_one/online_setting/input/"+row(0)+"/train")
        testData.rdd.coalesce(1,false).saveAsTextFile("/data/sidana/purch/experiments/atleast_one/online_setting/input/"+row(0)+"/test")
        }
    }
}
